<HEADLINE> At Least 15 People Killed in Peruvian Plane Crash </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Lima, march 29 (Xinhua) -- At least 15 people were killed in a
Peruvian air force plane crash which occurred in the northern city
of Piura on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
According to Local media, the plane was carrying at 40
passengers, most of them believed to be civilians.  
</P>
