<HEADLINE> URGENT: Explosion Kills 2 in Ramallah, Palestine </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, March 29 (Xinhua) -- An explosion in the West Bank
town of Ramallah Sunday night killed two people and injured some
others, Israel's army radio said.
</P>
<P>
The explosion occurred near the office of Jibril Rajoub, who
is the Palestinian official in charge of preventive security in
the West Bank, the radio said
</P>
<P>
