<HEADLINE> Chinese Senior Official on Macao SAR Preparatory Committee </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The deputy director denies any possibility that the committee
will interfere in the administration of the current Macao
Government, saying it will constitute no second power center in
Macao as it is only responsible for the establishment of the Macao
SAR.
</P>
<P>
