China's reunification and said the Chinese government treasures
the traditional friendship.
</P>
<P>
At the turn of the century, he said, China is ready to make a
concerted effort with Mozambique to develop long-term, stable and
all-round cooperative relations oriented towards the 21st century
in the interests of the two peoples.
</P>
<P>
Chissano said that his government places great importance on
relations with China. Since diplomatic ties were established,
bilateral friendly ties of cooperation have got increasingly close
and the friendship between the two peoples continues to deepen.
</P>
<P>
